videos.description: Napheesa Collier swiftly blows by a Duquesne defender to make an easy layup for UConn.
videos.headline: Collier speeds past defender for the layup

videos.description: Azura Stevens uses her height to swat Duquesne's Conor Richardson shot out of bounds.
videos.headline: Stevens emphatically blocks shot

videos.description: UConn's Napheesa Collier steals Duquesne's Eniko Kuttor's pass and takes it home for a layup.
videos.headline: Collier steals and scores
